videos.description: On the first possession of the game Baylor's Jalen Pitre gets a sack in the end zone for a safety.
videos.headline: Baylor opens game with a safety

videos.description: Charlie Brewer finds Blake Lynch who takes it 54-yards for a Baylor touchdown.
videos.headline: Lynch goes up the sideline for 54-yard TD

videos.description: Mat Boesen forces a Charlie Brewer fumble that is recovered for TCU by Nick Orr.
videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer coughs it up

videos.description: Kenny Hill hits Jarrison Stewart in the back of the end zone to give TCU a 14-9 lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: Stewart grabs 7-yard TD for TCU

videos.description: Sewo Olonilua runs for a 32-yard touchdown to extend the Horned Frogs' lead over Baylor.
videos.headline: TCU's Olonilua goes untouched for TD

videos.description: Trestan Ebner takes the Charlie Brewer pass in the flat 58 yards for a Baylor touchdown.
videos.headline: Baylor's Ebner takes off for 58-yard TD

videos.description: Desmon White extends the ball over the pylon  for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: TCU's White reaches for TD

videos.description: Kenny Hill hits Jalen Reagor on a screen pass who takes it to the house.
videos.headline: TCU's Raegor takes screen for 30-yard TD

videos.description: After a massive fight breaks out and both Baylor's and TCU's benches clear, the refs give everyone on the benches and on the field an unsportsmanlike penalty.
videos.headline: Entire Baylor, TCU, teams receive personal foul after brawl

videos.description: Kenny Hill keeps it on an option run and scores a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: TCU's Hill scores on QB keeper
